    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "note_text",
      "x": 310,
      "y": 735,
      "width": 620,
      "height": 70,
      "text": "🧠 Key Pattern: Think Tool for Self-Verification\n   Before executing any tool, Agent calls Think Tool to:\n   1. Verify correct tool selection\n   2. Check required parameters\n   3. Plan multi-step sequences\n   4. Prevent hallucinated emails/actions\n\n🔄 Multi-LLM Strategy: Route task to best model (GPT for tools, Claude for writing, DeepSeek for reasoning)",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "strokeColor": "#92400e",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "originalText": "🧠 Key Pattern: Think Tool for Self-Verification\n   Before executing any tool, Agent calls Think Tool to:\n   1. Verify correct tool selection\n   2. Check required parameters\n   3. Plan multi-step sequences\n   4. Prevent hallucinated emails/actions\n\n🔄 Multi-LLM Strategy: Route task to best model (GPT for tools, Claude for writing, DeepSeek for reasoning)",
      "autoResize": true
